cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.GR, cs.MM

This paper deals with the problem of 3D human pose estimation from single images using deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a method to estimate camera pose jointly with human pose, which involves robotics and control, making cs.RO (Robotics) a likely category as well. The use of deep learning techniques and large datasets also suggests that cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category. The paper also mentions a new Ski dataset, which involves motion capture and could be categorized under cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
